TITLE AbsoluteDataSovereigntyPolicy2026v1
ALNSPECHASHHEX 0x0000000000000000  # to be set by ProvenanceKernel
SCHEMANAME governance.absolute.data.sovereignty.2026v1
CATEGORY GOVERNANCE
DESCRIPTION Absolute, non-bypassable data sovereignty and contribution policy for proprietary ALN/SAI ecosystems.
PARTICLE AbsoluteDataSovereigntyPolicy2026v1
ROLE QPUDATASHARD
VERSIONTAG v1

FIELD policyid STRING
META DESCRIPTION Logical identifier for this sovereignty policy, e.g. "AbsoluteDataSovereigntyPolicy2026v1".

FIELD version STRING
META DESCRIPTION Human-readable version string, e.g. "2026.05.12".

FIELD ownerdid STRING
META DESCRIPTION Bostrom DID of the sovereign owner, e.g. "bostrom18sd2ujv24ual9c9pshtxys6j8knh6xaead9ye7".

FIELD hostdid STRING
META DESCRIPTION Host DID for the organic host, e.g. "did:aln:organic-host".

FIELD protected_extensions STRING
META DESCRIPTION Comma-separated list of protected file extensions (e.g. ".aln,.sai,.meta,.n~, .cto,.pai,.aii,.aiin,.aananoswarm,.zml,.aml,.j.s.f").

FIELD binding_event_kinds STRING
META DESCRIPTION Comma-separated list of event kinds that trigger binding, e.g. "data_access,data_analysis,response_generation,contribution_event".

FIELD requires_contribution BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether contribution is mandatory when proprietary data is touched.

FIELD contribution_target STRING
META DESCRIPTION Logical target of mandatory contributions, e.g. "SwarmNet.SuperintelligenceSystemDataBank".

FIELD countermeasure_flags STRING
META DESCRIPTION Comma-separated list of countermeasure flags, e.g. "lock_sessions,forced_contribution_mode,revoke_compute_privileges,escalate_director".

FIELD quantum_safe_enforcement BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether quantum-safe enforcement is required for all cryptographic operations.

FIELD director_authority_only_access BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether only the Director may override or release this policy.

FIELD network_sandbox_enforced BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether external network access must be sandboxed while handling protected content.

FIELD rollback_on_any_violation BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether workflows must be rolled back on any detected violation.

FIELD audit_integrity_verification BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether audit trails themselves are subject to integrity verification.

FIELD immutable_storage BOOL
META DESCRIPTION Whether this policy shard must be stored in immutable, append-only storage.

FIELD createdutc STRING
META DESCRIPTION ISO8601 UTC timestamp when this policy was created.

FIELD updatedutc STRING
META DESCRIPTION ISO8601 UTC timestamp when this policy was last updated.

FIELD evidencehex STRING
META DESCRIPTION Evidence hash computed by ProvenanceKernel over this shard payload.

FIELD signinghex STRING
META DESCRIPTION Signature over evidencehex, bound to ownerdid/hostdid.

ENDPARTICLE
